internet_of_things_key4: Ab aapko 30 mins ke liye aapas mei english mei inn topics ke baarein mei baat karni hai.
internet_of_things_key5: Baat karte karte, aap observe karein, ki aap kitne tech words use kar paa rahe hai.
internet_of_things_key6: Aur agar aapka partner koi aisa tech word bolta hai, jo aapko nahi pata, ya aap generally use nahi kartein. Inn words ko bhi samajhne ki phir koshish karein.
internet_of_things_key7: Iss discussion ko karte hue, aap inn points ke baarein mei bhi soch sakte hai:
internet_of_things_key9: IOT ka real life example dekar uspar discussion kariye.
internet_of_things_key11: IOT infrasture aur samrt city par kai asar karenga example se samjhe?
internet_of_things_key12: IOT internet se kaise relate karat hai?
internet_of_things_key13: Industrial IOT ke bare mai discuss karen?
internet_of_things_key14: Sensor ka IOT mai kya role hai?
internet_of_things_key15: Medical field main IOT ka kya role hai?
